data.description: Introducing a charming three-bedroom, two-bathroom villa, nestled in the picturesque Summerbrooke neighborhood.   The Summerbrooke community offers great amenities to include a pool, gym, dog park, basketball courts and more. This beautiful home in the heart of Mount Dora features an inviting open floorplan, with split bedrooms, high ceilings and sits on a premium lot with no rear neighbors. The spacious kitchen boasts contemporary amenities, granite countertops, ample storage and stainless steel appliances.  Each of the three bedrooms is generously sized and designed for optimal comfort, while the master suite features an ensuite bathroom for added convenience. The outdoor space features a covered patio with no rear neighbors and space for entertaining. Additionally, the property includes a two-car garage and is located within easy reach of schools, shopping, parks, major highways and less than 10 mins from Downtown Mount Dora and approximately 40 mins to Downtown Orlando.  Don't miss the chance to make this exceptional property your forever home. Ask your lender regarding the USDA program which can get you into this property with "zero" money down". Seller will assist with closing costs.
